reviews.review_text: Should have Known, Charlie Miller I won't wast time. Good Lovin' is awesome, quality is impeccable. Good work brother.
4-6-78 Very good show. Grate sound quality once you get past the aud patch of Bertha.

Not the pick of the litter This and the night after are some slower-unrefined moments of the spring.

Estimated is descent.

4-8-78 is phenomenal
